movie.title: Battle in Space: The Armada Attacks
movie.title_english: Battle in Space: The Armada Attacks
movie.title_long: Battle in Space: The Armada Attacks (2021)
movie.description_intro: A series of shorts depicting a future in 2420 after aliens and powerful space wizards enslaved human villages until a group of rebels organize a counter attack against their alien overlords by piloting fully loaded spaceships.

movies.title: Anna 2
movies.summary: Starring Justin Duncan, Gerald Crum, Mercedes Peterson and John Charles Dickson. The Stars of two competing and colliding paranormal television shows converge on an abandoned haunted amusement park which ends up being the epicenter to hell. They are now all trapped - in an all out war against pure evil.

movies.title: Buck Wild
movies.summary: The comrades Craig Thompson, Jerry, Lance and Tom Alexander travel to the Buck Wild Farm in Texas to spend vacation hunting deer. Soon they discover that the owner Clyde was bitten by a Chupacabra and has infected his slut daughter Candy and neighbors that now are zombies. Will they survive?

movies.title: Deathcember
movies.summary: A collection of 24 films that take a look at the dark side of the festive season. 24 international directors with the most diverse ideas and styles; linked by short animated segments that deal with the Advent calendar itself.
